charges.charge_description: 8:1326A.F REENTRY OF DEPORTED ALIENS - defendant, who had been previously deported, entered, attempted to enter, and was found in the United States in violation of Title 8, USC 1326(a).(1)

charges.charge_disposition: It is ordered the defendant shall pay a special assessment of $100.00. The defendant is placed on probation for 3 years.

charges.charge_description: 8:1326 - On or about December 28, 2011 in Crane County, in the Western District of Texas, defendant, an alien who had previously been deported, did illegally re-enter the United States in violation of Title 8, USC 1326(a).
